      "text": "Lesson 38",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 0.31,
      "endTime": 2.22,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Lesson",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "课程，第...课"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The first calendar",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.23,
      "endTime": 9.57
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What is the importance of the dots, lines, and symbols engraved on stone, bones and ivory?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.58,
      "endTime": 20.51,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Future historians will be in a unique position when they come to record the history of our own times.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 20.52,
      "endTime": 28.57,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They will hardly know which facts to select from the great mass of evidence that steadily accumulates.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.58,
      "endTime": 37.06,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What is more, they will not have to rely solely on the written word.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 37.07,
      "endTime": 42.24,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Films, videos, CDs and CD-ROMs are just some of the bewildering amount of information they will have.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 42.25,
      "endTime": 52.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They will be able, as it were, to see and hear us in action.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 52.41,
      "endTime": 58.89,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But the historian attempting to reconstruct the distant past is always faced with a difficult task.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 58.9,
      "endTime": 66.99,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He has to deduce what he can from the few scanty clues available.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 67,
      "endTime": 72.6,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Even seemingly insignificant remains can shed interesting light on the history of early man.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 72.61,
      "endTime": 80.68,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Up to now, historians have assumed that calendars came into being with the advent of agriculture,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.69,
      "endTime": 88.66,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "for then man was faced with a real need to understand something about the seasons.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 88.67,
      "endTime": 95.54,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Recent scientific evidence seems to indicate that this assumption is incorrect.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 95.55,
      "endTime": 103,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Historians have long been puzzled by dots, lines and symbols which have been engraved on walls, bones, and the ivory tusks of mammoths.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 103.01,
      "endTime": 114.97
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The nomads who made these markings lived by hunting and fishing during the last Ice Age which began about 35, 000 B.C. and ended about 10, 000 B.C.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 114.98,
      "endTime": 129.26
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "By correlating markings made in various parts of the world,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 129.27,
      "endTime": 133.8
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "historians have been able to read this difficult code.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 133.81,
      "endTime": 138.1,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They have found that it is connected with the passage of days and the phases of the moon.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 138.11,
      "endTime": 144.48,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It is, in fact, a primitive type of calendar.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 144.49,
      "endTime": 149.24,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It has long been known that the hunting scenes depicted on walls were not simply a form of artistic expression.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 149.25,
      "endTime": 157.39,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They had a definite meaning, for they were as near as early man could get to writing.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 157.4,
      "endTime": 163.93,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It is possible that there is a definite relation between these paintings and the markings that sometimes accompany them.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 163.94,
      "endTime": 173.57,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It seems that man was making a real effort to understand the seasons 20, 000 years earlier than has been supposed.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 173.58,
      "endTime": 178.58,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
